{"tid":110912,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"( 一天都光哂 ) 大師午間教路：利淡因素浮現","createTime":"2017-02-07T05:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T11:12:54.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5777fe056b241bf8d31697f212d9b4bf5abfb4ab","tid":110912,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"沈振盈<br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁<br />\n大師午間教路：利淡因素浮現<br />\n<br />\n訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈指，現時有很多不尋常走勢，例如金價飆升，公用股股價又緩緩上 <br />\n升，雖然金市傳養老金入市，但他認為過去已傳多次，但最後都沒有落實，不建議現時衝入市。 <br />\n<br />\n大師又認為，港股主要受外圍因素影響，利淡因素開始浮現，建議現時宜減磅，不要太進取。"},{"pid":"c440c80e8730a36a62fa6c8d164e7a663514451f","tid":110912,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"無大師圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"75b6f73fff91cf2b3849d2df06ec1abeddadd6b6","tid":110912,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"( 一天都光哂 ) ???"},{"pid":"483dca4ab49867692287b4849f0fc58426ac3eba","tid":110912,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:19:33.000Z","msg":"掂呀，睇尾市倒升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db028fe789ec181a949b08ae1f8fc886f7425b0","tid":110912,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無大師圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/eb7783.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Feb7783.gif&h=3560e057&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f38652bbdeb3cdd730895beff4824de46eb8c718","tid":110912,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/9ea4d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/